{"tid":1098294,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《星際牛仔》公佈主演名單","createTime":"2019-04-09T03:16:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-09T07:44:19.000Z","uid":64191,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3d85a3408391df31ba2640fefb0f5effc0b2872c","tid":1098294,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T03:16:43.000Z","msg":"改編日本科幻動畫《星際牛仔》（Cowboy Bebop）的真人版影集在 2017 年夏天釋出製作資訊後，去年秋天確定落腳線上影音串流平台 Netflix ，日前 Netflix 則釋出了幾位主要角色的演出卡司名單。<br />\n<br />\n《星際牛仔》真人版影集將由趙約翰（John Cho）飾演史派克（Spike）、穆斯塔法夏奇爾（Mustafa Shakir）飾演傑特（Jet）、 丹妮拉皮內達（Daniella Pineda）飾演菲（Faye）、艾力克斯哈塞爾（Alex Hassell）飾演威夏斯（Vicious）。<br />\n<br />\n《星際牛仔》故事主要描述四人一狗的一幫賞金獵人在銀河中穿梭的冒險旅程，而真人版影集首集將由《雷神索爾3：諸神黃昏》（Thor: Ragnarok）編劇克里斯優斯特（Chris Yost）執筆劇本、執導過多部漫威影集的艾力克斯賈西亞洛培茲（Alex Garcia Lopez）執導，原動畫導演渡邊信一郎也將擔任顧問。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hypesphere.com/news/16517\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hypesphere.com%2Fnews%2F16517&d=Srnh2QCYUB68P60bIi3tLSZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=0a4ea72c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hypesphere.com/news/16517</a><br />\n<br />\nSpike由The searching既主演擔任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nFaye冇左大奶奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nJet變黑人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nVicious變左鬍鬚佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n問題係Ed同Ein會係點演呢？"},{"pid":"5e5f630f75aab1fe6c53ec14b932417636e43811","tid":1098294,"uid":159266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T03:52:14.000Z","msg":"Milf<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b15ff308102bc84a5f67e60b58618b562c5502d2","tid":1098294,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5e5f630f75aab1fe6c53ec14b932417636e43811","tid":1098294,"uid":159266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T03:52:14.000Z","msg":"Milf<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T03:53:22.000Z","msg":"milf!"},{"pid":"b911853a1834232586102b4438a3cfe231c333e5","tid":1098294,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T03:54:55.000Z","msg":"通常日本動漫被荷里活拍真人版都拍到走晒樣, 唔會睇囉"},{"pid":"ce9dc3fb2a5e279457b99b619627027dd2dc7423","tid":1098294,"uid":2781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T04:37:18.000Z","msg":"呢套動畫好好睇喎，我宜家仲記得當時開場音樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7442aa96f32fd63a75606de7050749fe63b83d41","tid":1098294,"uid":70448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T07:44:19.000Z","msg":"音樂呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重點之一喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}